_json.title: How to achieve flawless stencil  look on furniture. Stenciling technique.
_json.gridTitle: How to achieve flawless stencil  look on furniture. Stenciling technique.
_json.description:
How to-
 • Secure stencil with a painters tape or spray adhesive glue 
 • Roll your Redesign with Prima roller in chalk paint and lightly roll over stencil 
 • Slowly remove the stencil and repeat 
 • Seal it with clear coat once dry. 

Products used
 • Redesign with Prima stencil Midcentury Vibes
 • Redesign with Prima roller
 • Mud Paint chalk paint Just Black 
 • Painters tape 

All products are available on my website. 

Finished piece can be seen on my Facebook and Instagram page Click2Restore
